les/?book=14&chapter=16&verse=9'>2Ch 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=34&verse=7'>Psa 34:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=41&verse=2'>Psa 41:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=91&verse=4'>Psa 91:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=125&verse=2'>Psa 125:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=2&verse=5'>Zec 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=21&verse=18'>Luk 21:18</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Security, SECURITY<p/>Divine Keeper, PROVIDENCE DIVINE<p/>Fear Not, ENCOURAGEMENT<p/><b>(2) Examples of</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=5'>Gen 35:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=14&verse=20'>Exo 14:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=17'>2Ki 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=31'>Ezr 8:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=6&verse=22'>Dan 6:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=7&verse=3'>Rev 7:3</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Preservation, PROVIDENCE DIVINE<p/><b>(F) DIVINE PROTECTOR,</b> God represented as protector of his people<p/>under the following types and figures.<p/><b>(a) God of Battles</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=14&verse=14'>Exo 14:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=27'>Exo 23:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=30'>Deu 1:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=22'>Deu 3:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=24'>2Sa 5:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=29'>2Ch 20:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=32&verse=8'>2Ch 32:8</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.